    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor? This beauty is in absolute mint condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It\u2019s incredibly clean, runs like a dream, and I promise you\u2019ll be hard-pressed to find a single speck of dust on it. I'm sad to see it go, but it's totally ready for its next adventure with you. Shoot me a message if you want to come check it out in person!",
