    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade BMW E46 M3 in museum-quality condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain is mated to a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Mechanically, this chassis is beyond reproach: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings and VANOS system have been overhauled to exceed OEM specifications. The suspension retains its factory-correct damping profiles with zero bushing deflection. Finished in a flawless exterior with a pristine interior, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. No leaks, no codes, and a perfectly indexed service history.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
