    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, boasting its original, deep-gloss factory paint that has been meticulously ceramic coated and shielded from the elements in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin retains its factory-fresh scent and supple leather texture, with absolutely zero signs of bolster wear, carpet staining, or UV fading on the dashboard. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, and I have a complete, chronological binder of every receipt and inspection report since new. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that looks, smells, and drives like a brand-new car.",
